[CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/rakai-warned-by-police-after-calling-911-over-bad-haircut-during-live-stream/articleshow/132591629.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T02:27:54+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132591625,imgsize-605005.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by George Washington: 'Associate yourself with Men of good Quality if you...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132591541.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[George Washington's dedication to personal growth greatly influenced his leadership style. He recognized that surrounding oneself with positive individuals enhances one's reputation. This idea is supported by both ancient philosophers and contemporary studies on social dynamics. In today's workplaces and digital spaces, making thoughtful choices in your associations is crucial for protecting your judgment and shaping your future positively.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-george-washington-associate-yourself-with-men-of-good-quality-if-you-esteem-your-own-reputation-and-why-people-around-you-shape-the-person-you-become/articleshow/132591541.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/quote-of-the-day-by-george-washington-associate-yourself-with-men-of-good-quality-if-you-esteem-your-own-reputation-and-why-people-around-you-shape-the-person-you-become/articleshow/132591541.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T02:27:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132591624,imgsize-361508.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Quote of the day by Mieko Kamiya, mother of ikigai: 'We did not create the morning... The meaning of life is like the morning']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132591580.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-mieko-kamiya-mother-of-ikigai-we-did-not-create-the-morning-the-meaning-of-life-is-like-the-morning/articleshow/132591580.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/quote-of-the-day-by-mieko-kamiya-mother-of-ikigai-we-did-not-create-the-morning-the-meaning-of-life-is-like-the-morning/articleshow/132591580.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-24T02:11:51+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132591588,imgsize-49386.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Celeste Rivas' clothing presented as new evidence in D4vd preliminary hearing]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132591556.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[During D4vd's preliminary hearing, a forensic expert described the poor condition of Celeste Rivas' clothing, calling it heavily soiled, wet, and covered with insects. The court also heard testimony about evidence found in D4vd's Tesla and garage, along with details of his earnings in 2025. Prosecutors continue presenting evidence as the court decides whether the case will proceed to trial.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/celeste-rivas-clothing-presented-as-new-evidence-in-d4vd-preliminary-hearing/articleshow/132591556.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/celeste-rivas-clothing-presented-as-new-evidence-in-d4vd-preliminary-hearing/article